### 健康检查
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/health

### 景点列表（Unity 自动讲解映射）
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1/spots

### 单景点个性化讲解生成（节点到达触发）
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1/guide/spot-generate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "node_id": "library",
  "user_profile": "new_student",
  "style": "friendly",
  "language": "zh"
}

### 路线规划
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1/route/plan
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "start_id": "gate_north",
  "end_id": "stadium",
  "avoid_crowded": true,
  "prefer_indoor": false
}

### 生成讲解
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1/guide/generate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_profile": "new_student",
  "style": "storytelling",
  "language": "zh",
  "route_nodes": ["gate_north", "library", "teaching_a", "stadium"]
}

### 导览问答
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1/session/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "这个景点对新生有什么帮助？",
  "language": "zh",
  "current_spot_id": "library"
}

### 文本转语音
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1/speech/tts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "text": "欢迎来到图书馆，这里是学校重要的学习中心。",
  "voice": "xiaoyan"
}

### 语音识别 ASR（请将文件路径替换为本地 wav 文件）
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1/speech/asr
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=WebAppBoundary

--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="language"

zh
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="audio"; filename="question.wav"
Content-Type: audio/wav

< ./question.wav
--WebAppBoundary--

### 语音问答（ASR + Chat）
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1/session/voice-chat
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=WebAppBoundary

--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="language"

zh
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="current_spot_id"

library
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="audio"; filename="question.wav"
Content-Type: audio/wav

< ./question.wav
--WebAppBoundary--
